-- EBRD Buys RusHydro Ruble Eurobonds to Help `Internationalize' Currency
-- B y   D e n i s   M a t e r n o v s k y
-- 2010-10-22T10:41:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-22/ebrd-buys-rushydro-ruble-eurobonds-to-help-internationalize-currency.html
The European Bank for Reconstruction
and Development said it bought 22.5 percent of 0A0 RusHydro’s
debut Eurobond denominated in rubles to support the government’s
push to “internationalize” its currency.  The EBRD bought 4.5 billion rubles ($147 million) of the
notes sold yesterday, the bank said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
